query:
INSERT INTO materialItems (materialId, title, type, url, `order`, createdAt)
SELECT 
  m.id as materialId,
  mat.titulo as title,
  mat.tipo as type,
  mat.url as url,
  0 as `order`,
  NOW() as createdAt
FROM materiais mat
JOIN materials m ON m.title = mat.titulo
WHERE mat.url IS NOT NULL;
